definitions.definition: Issuing or emerging from something, especially from the bottom (or a division) of the field or chief, or from an ordinary.
Having only the upper half depicted, especially if because it is issuing from something (such as a division of the field). ( Compare naissant . )
definitions.label_groups: heraldry , by extension , of an animal
